Violet, Countess of Grantham may be coming back in the new American show The Gilded Age from Downton creator Julian Fellowes . 
  Made by the US network NBC, the show will be set among the high society families of New York in the late 19th Century . 
  Played by Dame Maggie Smith in the ITV drama, Violet will be seen as her younger self . 
  There may also be a place for Robert and American-born Cora . 
 